www.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-economist-who-called-2008-recession-mega-bubble-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongtime%20market%20bear%20David%20Rosenberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20coming%20around%20after%20this%20year's%20blistering%20stock%20market%20rally.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20says%20his%20updated%20view%20doesn't%20amount%20to%20%26quot%3Bthrowing%20in%20the%20towel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20admits%20that%20the%20technology-fueled%20AI%20boom%20is%20requiring%20him%20to%20reframe%20his%20thinking%20on%20the%20broader%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20high%20time%20for%20me%20to%20stop%20pontificating%20on%20all%20the%20reasons%20why%20the%20U.S.%20stock%20market%20is%20crazily%20overvalued%20and%20all%20the%20reasons%20to%20be%20bearish%20based%20on%20all%20the%20variables%20I%20have%20relied%20on%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20wrote%20to%20his%20clients%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%20has%20long%20relied%20on%20today's%20stock%20market%20valuations%20relative%20to%20the%20past%20to%20highlight%20just%20how%20historically%20extreme%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20currently%20valued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20he's%20not%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELongtime%20stock%20bull%20Ed%20Yardeni%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-charts-stretched-sp500-valuations-buffett-ratio-yields-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighlighted%20five%20charts%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20that%20showed%20that%20valuations%20have%20been%20stretched%20to%20historical%20extremes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20Rosenberg%2C%20the%20extreme%20valuations%20may%20actually%20be%20warranted%20if%20AI%20can%20unleash%20a%20wave%20of%20productivity%20upon%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20idea%20was%20echoed%20by%20BlackRock%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-blackrock-