attack%20was%20racially%20motivated%2C%20her%20suit%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228320b8bf-28be-47b1-b8c6-7bccc6b7a885%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarch%2015-16%2C%202024%3A%20Straub%20told%20Fleming%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bshutting%20down%20Miss%20America%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStraub's%20threat%20came%20a%20day%20after%20Fleming%20declined%20to%20serve%20as%20his%20proxy%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20board%20members%20of%20their%20gated%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStraub%20told%20Fleming%20he%20wanted%20to%20end%20Miss%20America%20because%20she%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20be%20controlled%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20organization%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bwaste%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20said%20Fleming%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bfailure%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bover%20the%20hill%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20would%20bring%20her%20children%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20humiliation%26quot%3B%20and%20send%20letters%20to%20all%20the%20Miss%20America%20state%20directors%20saying%20she%20was%20mentally%20ill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20day%2C%20Straub%20sent%20Fleming%20a%20letter%20notifying%20her%20of%20her%20%26quot%3BTemporary%20Suspension%20and%20Investigation%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20%26quot%3BMiss%20America%20Competitions%2C%20LLC.%26quot%3B%20Fleming%20said%20the%20letterhead%20featured%20typos%20in%20both%20the%20company%20name%20and%20the%20spelling%20of%20Fleming's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFleming%20said%20Straub%20also%20threatened%20to%20tie%20her%20up%20in%20%26quot%3Bthree%20years%20of%20civil%20litigation%26quot%3B%20unless%20she%20gave%20him%20%26quot%3Btotal%20control%20of%20Miss%20America%26quot%3B%20and%20promised%20to%20%26quot%3Balways%20be%20subservient%26quot%3B%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa2b60c8-a546-4ac5-bcbe-aab78cfb6e29%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EApril%2012%2C%202024%3A%20Straub%20gave%20Fleming%20what%20she%20says%20is%20a%20fraudulent%20Operating%20Agreement%20for%20Miss%20America%20Competition%2C%