ds%20credit%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I've%20been%20using%20them%20strategically%20to%20earn%20travel%20points%20and%20miles%20since%20after%20the%20birth%20of%20our%20first%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20days%20at%20home%20with%20our%20daughter%2C%20I%20learned%20how%20points%20and%20miles%20can%20be%20used%20for%20free%20or%20discounted%20travel.%20It%20meant%20we%20could%20still%20travel%20while%20operating%20on%20a%20budget%20with%20a%20single%20source%20of%20income.%20Since%20then%2C%20I've%20held%20several%20cards%20over%20the%20years%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-citi-credit-cards%5C%22%3ECiti%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-chase-card%5C%22%3EChase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-capital-one-credit-cards%5C%22%3ECapital%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%20branded%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20love%20the%20flexibility%20in%20point%20redemption%20that%20non-co-branded%20cards%20offer%2C%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20cards%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fplatinum-delta-amex-card-review%5C%22%3EDelta%20SkyMiles%C2%AE%20Platinum%20American%20Express%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20like%20it%20so%20much%20that%20we%20each%20have%20one.%20My%20favorite%20feature%20of%20the%20card%20is%20that%20it%20offers%20a%20complimentary%20companion%20pass%20each%20year.%20Because%20we%20have%20two%20kids%2C%20this%20means%20when%20we%20each%20purchase%20a%20ticket%2C%20we%20can%20then%20bring%20our%20children%20with%20us%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20fly%20to%20our%20vacation%20destinations%20at%20half-price%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20kids%2C%20now%20ages%205%20and%207%2C%20have%20traveled%20extensively%20around%20the%20U.S.%20Our%20Delta%20Platinum%20cards%20have%20made%20that%20possible.%20Each%20year%2C%20we%20use%20our%20companion%20passes%20to%20take%20a%20family%20vacation.%20We%20have%20been%20to%20Charleston%20once%20and%20Florida%20several%20times%20with%20them%20on%20these%20passes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20signed%20up%2C%20the%20annual%20fee%20was%20only%20%24250.%20We%20justified%20this%20price%20because%20regardless%20of%20where%20we%20flew%20with%20Delta%2C%20we%20weren't%20spending%20less%20than%20%24250%20on%20a%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmex%20recently%20increased%20the%20annual%20fee%20for%20the%20Delta%20Platinum%20to%20%24350%2Fyear%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20good%20value%20to%20us.%20The%20higher%20annual%20fee%20now%20allows%20you%20to%20use%20the%20companion%20pass%20for%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20Central%20America%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20and%20Alaska%2C%20whereas%20before%2C%20it%20only%20covered%20the%20lower%2048%20states.%20Since%20we%20live%20in%20Minnesota%2C%20we%20always%20have%20a%20warm%20winter%20getaway%20on%20our%20list%20for%20the%20winter%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20other%20perks%20offer%20added%20value%2C%20even%20if%20they%20aren't%20our%20top%20priority%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Delta%20Platinum%20card%20also%20offers%20other%20perks%20like%20discounted%20ticket%20bookings%20and%20additional%20points%20toward%20Medallion%20status.%20It%20also%20offers%20several%20statement%20credits%20you%20can%20enroll%20in%2C%20including%20%2410%20a%20month%20in%20rideshare%20credits%2C%20%2410%20a%20month%20Resy%20credits%2C%20and%20a%20%24150%20Delta%20Stays%20credit%20when%20using%20your%20credit%20card%20to%20book%20through%20the%20Delta%20Stays%20platform%20on%20delta.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20have%20yet%20to%20use%20the%20Delta%20Stays%20credit%2C%20I%20plan%20to%20do%20so%20in%20November%20this%20year.%20My%20husband%20travels%20a%20lot%20for%20work%20and%20enjoys%20earning%20Medallion%20status%2C%20which%20helps%20him%20get%20upgraded%20on%20flights.%20Even%20if%20we%20weren't%20to%20use%20any%20of%20the%20other%20credits%2C%20the%20annual%20fee%20pays%20for%20itself%20with%20the%20companion%20pass%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20time%20the%20companion%20pass%20wouldn't%20save%20you%20money%20is%20if%20you%20spend%20less%20than%20%24350%20per%20ticket%20on%20a%20flight.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20find%20tickets%20someplace%20domestically%20for%20%24300%2C%20it%20would%20cost%20you%20%241%2C200%20for%20a%20family%20of%20four.%20If%20you%20had%20two%20companion%20passes%2C%20you'd%20spend%20%24600%20for%20two%20tickets%20and%20get%20the%20other%20two%20free%20(besides%20taxes%20and%20fees)%2C%20but%20you%20also%20have%20to%20factor%20in%20the%20%24700%20you%20spent%20on%20the%20cards'%20annual%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstill-love-favorite-credit-card-even-after-annual-fee-increase-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733574602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6735259e192f525898584dbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstill-love-favorite-credit-card-even-after-annual-fee-increase-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20favorite%20credit%20card%20cuts%20the%20cost%20of%20my%20annual%20family%20vacation%20in%20half.%20Even%20though%20the%20price%20went%20up%2C%20that%20perk%20still%20makes%20it%20worthwhile.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Oelker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstill-love-favorite-credit-card-even-after-annual-fee-increase-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Shami%20Fitness%20Clearance%20Now%20%26quot%3BFormality%26quot%3B%2C%20To%20Play%20vs%20Aus%20From...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESenior%20India%20speedster%20Mohammed%20Shami%20is%20set%20to