-for-giving-her-a-double-mastectomy-at-14%2Farticleshow%2F116076541.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhy-this-ucla-student-is-suing-two-california-docs-for-giving-her-a-double-mastectomy-at-14%2Famp_articleshow%2F116076541.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhy-this-ucla-student-is-suing-two-california-docs-for-giving-her-a-double-mastectomy-at-14%2Famp_articleshow%2F116076541.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Moving%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Morocco%20taught%20me%20a%20different%20way%20of%20living.%20I%20sundry%20my%20clothes%20and%20consume%20less.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221537%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20posing%20in%20Morocco%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674751b09f2901eb60375e35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221153%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20moved%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Morocco%20five%20years%20ago.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20studied%20abroad%20in%20France%2C%20and%20since%20then%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20keep%20exploring%20the%20world.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20bought%20a%20one-way%20ticket%20to%20Morocco%20without%20knowing%20what%20to%20expect.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20don't%20have%20a%20dryer%20or%20a%20microwave%2C%20and%20I've%20adapted%20to%20a%20new%20way%20of%20living.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFive%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20booked%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-trip-to-morocco-five-star-hotels-paid-with-points-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eone-way%20ticket%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Morocco%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20no%20idea%20of%20what%20to%20expect.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'd%20spent%20several%20months%20prior%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-a-job-abroad-2017-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esearching%20for%20international%20job%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eopportunities%2C%20willing%20to%20go%20almost%20anywhere.%20I%20was%20surprised%20at%20how%20much%20I%20learned%20about%20living%20in%20my%20time%20in%20Meknes%2C%20where%20I%20now%20live.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba30dbe0-42d7-446e-9596-129862f58a69%5C%22%3EStudying%20abroad%20made%20me%20want%20to%20explore%20more%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20desire%20to%20move%20abroad%20stemmed%20from%20my%20search%20for%20the%20heightened%20discovery%20and%20immersion%20that%20I'd%20felt%20when%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiagnosed-epilepsy-seizures-studying-abroad-paris-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudied%20abroad%20in%20France%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20two%20years%20earlier.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20semester%20abroad%20was%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyu-student-hated-study-abroad-semester-florence-italy-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efirst%20trip%20outside%20the%20US%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20an%20experience%20that%20opened%20up%20the%20possibility%20of%20living%20abroad%20longer-term.%20In%20my%20senior%20year%20of%20college%2C%20I%20received%20job%20offers%20for%20positions%20in%20France%20and%20Morocco%20and%20decided%20on%20Morocco%20%E2%80%94%20somewhere%20new%2C%20in%20a%20part%20of%20the%20world%20with%20a%20culture%20I'd%20never%20experienced%20before.%20I%20planned%20to%20live%20there%20for%20a%20year%2C%20the%20length%20of%20my%20initial%20contract.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-travel-destinations-2019-lonely-planet-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egot%20to%20Meknes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20city%20where%20I'd%20be%20living%20and%20working%2C%20one%20of%20my%20new%20coworkers%20helped%20me%20find%20an%20apartment%20within%20days%20of%20my%20arrival.%20The%20apartment%20I%20rented%20didn't%20have%20all%20of%20the%20features%20I%20was%20used%20to%20%E2%80%94%20no%20dishwasher%2C%20clothes%20dryer%2C%20or%20microwave%20%E2%80%94%20and%20yet%20these%20amenities%20that%20felt%20so%20essential%20in%20the%20US%20didn't%20seem%20to%20matter%20in%20this%20new%20context.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2264932fd0-3094-4f47-bc58-147e08017b5e%5C%22%3EPeople%20jumped%20in%20to%20help%20me%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20my%20first%20week%20in%20my%20new%20apartment%20building%2C%20my%20downstairs%20neighbors%20stopped%20by%20with%20a%20bowl%20of%20fresh%20fruit%2C%20then%20offered%20to%20bring%20a%20couch%20from%20their%20first-floor%20apartment%20up%20to%20my%20fifth-floor%20apartment%20when%20they%20noticed%20I%20hadn't%20yet%20bought%20furniture.%20People%20I'd%20just%20met%20were%20constantly%20asking%20what%20I%20needed%20and%20offering%20to%20help%20as%20I%20got%20settled%20in.%20In%20my%20initial%20few%20months%20of%20adjusting%20to%20Moroccan%20culture%20and%20lifestyle%2C%20I%20learned%20from%20those%20around%20me%20about%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20maintain%20my%20home%2C%20where%20to%20run%20errands%2C%20and%20how%20to%20live%20in%20a%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20a%20dryer%2C%20I%20began%20to%20hang%20my%20clothes%20on%20the%20rooftop%20clotheslines.%20I%20let%20the%20sun%20do%20its%20work%2C%20no%20longer%20having%20to%20worry%20about%20clothes%20shrinking%20in%20the%20dryer%20or%20excessive%20heat%20wearing%20down%20the%20fabrics.%20Without%20a%20microwave%2C%20I%20reheated%20leftovers%20on%20the%20stove%20and%20found%20that%20my%20food%20tasted%20much%20better%20when%20I%20did%20so.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20shared%20many%20meals%20with%20others%20as%20neighbors%20invited%20me%20over%20for%20Friday%20couscous%20and%20tea.%20When%20Thanksgiving%20came%2C%20I%20hosted%20a%20dinner%20with%20classic%20Thanksgiving%20staples%3A%20roast%20meat%2C%20mashed%20potatoes%2C%20and%20pumpkin%20pie.%20Despite%20it%20being%20my%20first%20big%20holiday%20away%20from%20home%2C%20I%20felt%20at%20home%20in%20my%20newfound%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fcbf692b-2f19-4877-8753-1b7c0b56160c%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20started%20consuming%20differently%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20realized%20within%20my%20first%20few%20months%20that%20although%20the%20bigger%20supermarkets%20were%20the%20most%20convenient%20for%20grocery%20shopping%2C%20they%20weren't%20where%20I%20could%20get%20the%20best%20food.%20My%20grocery%20runs%20grew%20longer%20%E2%80%94%20a%20stop%20at%20the%20bakery%20for%20fresh%20bread%2C%20then%20to%20the%20produce%20stand%20for%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%2C%20then%20to%20the%20corner%20store%20to%20stock%20up%20on%20pantry%20staples.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20what%20some%20may%20consider%20an%20inconvenience%20of%20not%20having%20a%20car%20and%20making%20at%20least%20three%20stops%20to%20get%20what%20I%20need%20for%20the%20week%2C%20the%20benefit%20lies%20in%20all%20of%20these%20places%20being%20within%20a%2010-minute%20walk%20and%20the%20relationships%20I've%20formed%20with%20the%20shop%20owners%20as%20I%20come%20back%20week%20after%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20I've%20grown%20accustomed%20to%20the%20small%20differences%20in%20my%20daily%20lifestyle.%20As%20time%20has%20passed%2C%20I've%20come%20to%20understand%20and%20appreciate%20the%20bigger%20lifestyle%20differences%20as%20well.%20Especially%20around%20holidays%20in%20the%20US%2C%20consumerism%20dominates%20our%20buying%20culture.%20Stores%20regularly%20cycl