0arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20post%20on%20social%20media%20website%20X%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20from%20a%20handle%20named%20Khan%20Global%20Studies%2C%20demanded%20Mr%20Khan's%20release.%20Dr%20Anu%20Kumari%2C%20Sub-divisional%20police%20officer%20of%20Sachiwalaya%2C%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%2C%20misleading%20and%20provocative%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20statement%20came%20a%20day%20after%20police%20used%20mild%20lathicharge%20to%20disperse%20hundreds%20of%20protesting%20aspirants%20near%20the%20BPSC%20office%20in%20Patna%2C%20who%20were%20demanding%20withdrawal%20of%20%26quot%3Bchanges%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20rules%20for%20the%2070th%20BPSC%20Preliminary%20Examination%20scheduled%20for%20December%2013.%20The%20protesting%20students%20are%20demanding%20that%20exams%20be%20held%20in%20'One%20Shift%20and%20One%20Paper'%20to%20avoid%20the%20normalisation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BPSC%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20any%20changes%20to%20the%20examination%20process.%20The%20lathi%20charge%20on%20protesting%20candidates%20further%20escalated%20tensions%2C%20leading%20to%20public%20outrage%20and%20demands%20for%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducators%20like%20Mr%20Khan%20and%20and%20Motiur%20Rahman%20Khan%2C%20known%20as%20Guru%20Rahman%2C%20joined%20the%20protests%2C%20criticising%20the%20perceived%20lack%20of%20communication%20from%20BPSC%20and%20advocating%20for%20candidates'%20rights.%20However%2C%20tensions%20mounted%20as%20Mr%20Khan%20was%20seen%20going%20to%20a%20police%20station.%20Ms%20Kumari%20clarified%20that%20the%20educator%20came%20to%20the%20Gardanibagh%20police%20station%20on%20his%20own%20accord%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20later%20dropped%20to%20his%20vehicle%20near%20Atal%20Path%20in%20a%20police%20vehicle%20on%20his%20own%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20joining%20the%20aspirants%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20had%20said%20that%20with%20just%20a%20week%20left%20for%20exams%2C%20it%20was%20unfortunate%20that%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20protest%20for%20their%20demands%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bland%20of%20Chanakya%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20personal%20qualms%20with%20anyone.%20The%20process%20can%20be%20good%2C%20but%20the%20person%20implementing%20it%20should%20also%20be%20good.%20Can%20they%20assure%20us%20that%3F%20We%20will%20not%20move%20from%20here%20until%20normalisation%20is%20assured%20to%20be%20removed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20request%20the%20police%20administration%20to%20understand%20that%20your%20children%20are%20also%20studying%20here.%20We%20also%20teach%20them.%20We%20believe%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20That's%20why%20we%20are%20not%20protesting%20on%20the%20streets.%20We%20reached%20the%20Dharna-sthal%20(protesting%20site)%20to%20protest%20constitutionally.%20We%20will%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20normalisation%20(process)%20is%20cancelled.%20We%20don't%20have%20any%20expectations%20from%20BPSC.%20We%20have%20hopes%20from%20the%20government.%20We%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20politics.%20We%20will%20stand%20with%20those%20who%20will%20listen%20to%20our%20demands%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20Mr%20Khan%20further%20demanded%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20exam%20date%20and%20the%20acceptance%20of%20forms%20of%20students%20rejected%20due%20to%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20server.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%2C%20who%20was%20feeling%20unwell%2C%20has%20been%20admitted%20to%20Patna's%20Prabhat%20Memorial%20Hospital%2C%20Salman%20Haq%2C%20his%20associate%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20uproar%2C%20the%20BPSC%20issued%20a%20detailed%20clarification%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20'normalisation'%20process%20is%20neither%20mentioned%20in%20any%20clause%20of%20the%20advertisement%20for%20the%2070th%20Combined%20Preliminary%20Examination%20nor%20proposed%20afterwards.%20It%20affirmed%20that%20the%20exam%20will%20be%20conducted%20in%20a%20single%20shift%20on%20December%2013%2C%20202