0Ms%20Banerjee%20expressed%20frustration%20about%20the%20alliance's%20leadership%20and%20coordination.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20formed%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20now%20it%20is%20up%20to%20those%20leading%20the%20front%20to%20manage%20it.%20If%20they%20can't%20run%20the%20show%2C%20what%20can%20I%20do%3F%20I%20would%20just%20say%20that%20everyone%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20along%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20she%20herself%20hadn't%20taken%20charge%20of%20the%20bloc%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20given%20the%20opportunity%20I%20would%20ensure%20its%20smooth%20functioning.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20outside%20West%20Bengal%2C%20but%20I%20can%20run%20it%20from%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20comments%20quickly%20triggered%20speculations%20of%20her%20potentially%20leading%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20prompting%20clarification%20from%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20denied%20that%20Ms%20Banerjee%20sought%20leadership%20for%20personal%20ambition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20never%20said%20anything%20like%20this%2C%20she%20said%20she%20founded%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20that%20it%20was%20a%20necessary%20front%20against%20BJP.%20Her%20priority%20is%20West%20Bengal.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20a%20chair%20in%20Delhi.%20If%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20demands%20her%20leadership%2C%20she%20will%20do%20so%20from%20Kolkata%20only%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ghosh%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20prominent%20leaders%20from%20allied%20parties%20weighed%20in%20on%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20she%20means%20exactly%2C%20after%20the%20exit%20polls%20came%20out%20there%20was%20only%20one%20meeting%20of%20INDIA%20alliance.%20It%20is%20a%20fact%20but%20one%20should%20understand%20what%20is%20the%20objective%20of%20INDIA%20bloc.%20'Desh%20Bachao%2C%20BJP%20Hatao'%20this%20was%20a%20common%20resolve.%20Point%20here%20is%20the%20situation%20is%20not%20the%20same%20in%20every%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20CPI(M)%20leader%20D%20Raja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20seen%20as%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20responded%20cautiously%20to%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20remarks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20has%20her%20opinion%20and%20intent.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20Whatever%20conversations%20happen%2C%20it%20is%20natural%20that%20everyone%20will%20sit%20together%20and%20decide%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congress%20leader%20TS%20Singhdeo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rashid%20Alvi%20pointed%20to%20the%20need%20for%20consensus%20within%20the%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNitish%20Kumar%20also%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20lead%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20But%20in%20a%20coalition%20of%20this%20magnitude%2C%20leadership%20decisions%20are%20not%20made%20unilaterally.%20It%20requires%20agreement%20and%20consultation%20among%20all%20members.%20The%20bloc%20will%20collectively%20decide%20who%20will%20lead%2C%20who%20will%20be%20the%20convener%2C%20or%20if%20there%20will%20be%20a%20chairperson%2C%20who%20that%20person%20will%20be.%20It's%20natural%20for%20leaders%20to%20aspire%20to%20lead%2C%20but%20such%20decisions%20are%20not%20about%20individual%20ambitions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Tariq%20Anwar%20echoed%20this%20sentiment%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20a%20coalition%20of%20many%20parties%2C%20and%20leadership%20decisions%20will%20be%20made%20collectively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Congress%20MP%2C%20Tanuj%20Punia%2C%20said%20that%20these%20decisions%20should%20be%20discussed%20with%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20matter%20should%20be%20discussed%20with%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20and%20the%20party's%20National%20President.%20It's%20not%20something%20to%20be%20debated%20in%20the%20media.%20If%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20suggestions%2C%20they%20should%20be%20presented%20for%20discussion%20among%20all%20member%20parties%2C%20and%20decisions%20will%20be%20taken%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20INDIA%20partners%20Congress%20and%20CPI(M)%20expressed%20caution%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Udaiveer%20Singh%20voiced%20support%20for%20Ms%20Banerjee%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20is%20a%20senior%20leader%2C%20she%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20experience.%20She%20is%20capable.%20Our%20party's%20relationship%20with%20her%20is%20good%20and%20we%20have%20trust%20in%20her%20leadership.%20INDIA%20bloc%20leaders%20together%20need%20to%20decide%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%20If%20such%20a%20decision%20is%20taken%2C%20we%20will%20support%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC's%20dominance%20in%20West%20Bengal%20has%20bolstered%20its%20position%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20Recent%20bypoll%20victories%2C%20including%20defeating%20the%20BJP%2C%20have%20reinforced%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20stature%20as%20a%20formidable%20anti-BJP%20force.%20However%2C%20internal%20differences%20within%20the%20bloc%20and%20criticism%20over%20coordination%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20its%20effectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%20MP%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20recently%20urged%20Congress%20and%20other%20INDIA%20bloc%20allies%20to%20set%20aside%20egos%20and%20recognise%20Ms%20Banerjee%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20which%20comprises%20over%20two%20dozen%20opposition%20parties%2C%20was%20formed%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP's%20dominance.%20However%2C%20internal%20divisions%20and%20the%20competing%20ambitions%20of%20its%20leaders%20posed%20challenges%20which%20reflected%20in%20election%20results%20in%20states%20like%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%