0(Samajwadi%20Party%20president)%20Akhilesh%20Singh%20Yadav.%20If%20anyone%20in%20the%20MVA%20speaks%20such%20language%2C%20what%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20them%3F%20Why%20should%20we%20stay%20with%20them%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20two%20Samajwadi%20Party%20wins%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20contested%20103%20seats%20but%20managed%20to%20win%20only%2016.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20which%20fielded%20candidates%20in%2089%20constituencies%2C%20won%2020%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20NCP%2C%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20contested%2087%20seats%20and%20secured%20victory%20in%20just%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMilind%20Narvekar%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20party%2C%20posted%20a%20tweet%2C%20and%20we%20have%20only%20responded%20to%20him.%20The%20MVA%20was%20formed%20on%20two%20key%20principles%3A%20protecting%20the%20Constitution%20and%20upholding%20secular%20values.%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20received%20votes%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20MVA%2C%20with%20support%20from%20people%20of%20all%20religions%20and%20secular-minded%20individuals%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Samajwadi%20leader%20Rais%20Shaikh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahayuti%20alliance%2C%20comprising%20the%20BJP%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%2C%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20faction%2C%20won%20230%20of%20the%20288%20seats.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20swearing-in%20of%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20with%20Mr%20Shinde%20and%20Mr%20Pawar%20taking%20oath%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20on%20December%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShiv%20Sena%20should%20reflect%20on%20this.%20A%20minimum%20understanding%20was%20established%20to%20set%20aside%20radical%20Hindu%20ideologies%2C%20but%20if%20such%20a%20radical%20stance%20is%20adopted%2C%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20others%20will%20need%20to%20reconsider%20their%20position.%20This%20is%20our%20perspective.%20We%20want%20Uddhav's%20Shiv%20Sena%20to%20address%20this%20issue%20and%20clarify%20why%20such%20sentiments%20are%20being%20expressed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shaikh%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewly-elected%20MLAs%20of%20the%20MVA%20alliance%20staged%20a%20walkout%20during%20the%20Maharashtra%20Legislative%20Assembly's%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20today%2C%20alleging%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20coalition's%20victory%20was%20engineered%20through%20manipulation%20of%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMVA%20leaders%20gathered%20near%20the%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20statue%20at%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20to%20explain%20their%20stance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20boycotted%20the%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20today%20as%20democracy%20is%20being%20murdered%20by%20the%20use%20of%20EVMs.%20This%20(the%20results%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections)%20is%20not%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20public%20it%20is%20the%20mandate%20of%20EVM%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aditya%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20senior%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20including%20Nana%20Patole%20of%20Congress%20and%20Jitendra%20Awhad%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20echoed%20concerns%20over%20what%20they%20termed%20an%20%26quot%3Bundemocratic%20attitude%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20and%20reiterated%20demands%20for%20elections%20to%20be%20conducted%20using%20ballot%20papers%20instead%20of%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733570760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fo117pvqo_akhilesh-uddhav-1200_625x300_07_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsamajwadi-party-exits-maha-vikas-aghadi-after-uddhav-thackeray-aides-remark-on-babri-mosque-demolition-7193272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20blow%20to%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20and%20the%2