s%20a%20Sunni%20majority%20with%20a%20significant%20presence%20of%20Shias%2C%20Druze%20and%20Syrian%20Christians.%20Being%20an%20ethnic%20Kaleidoscope%20has%20made%20it%20vulnerable%20to%20sectarian%20tensions%20and%20foreign%20sponsors'%20manipulation%20causing%20instability%20since%20the%20Crusades%20in%20the%20medieval%20era.%20It%20is%20at%20a%20civilisation%20faultline%20straddling%20three%20Sunni%20blocks%3A%20Turkey%2C%20Egypt%20and%20the%20Gulf%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20bridge%20between%20Shia-majority%20Lebanon%2C%20Iraq%20and%20Iran.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%2013-Year-Long%20Civil%20War%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Al-Assad%20family%20of%20the%20Alawi%20sect%20of%20Shia%20Islam%20has%20ruled%20Syria%20for%20over%2050%20years.%20The%20regime%20formally%20professes%20to%20Ba'ath%20party%20ideology%20of%20Pan-Arab%20nationalism.%20It%20has%20faced%20Arab%20Spring's%20most%20persistent%20and%20bloody%20politico-military%20insurrection%20since%202011%2C%20which%20has%20killed%20up%20to%20half%20a%20million%20Syrians%2C%20displaced%207%20million%20internally%20and%20forced%206.4%20million%20into%20exile%20abroad%20from%20the%20country's%2023.5%20million%20population.%20The%2013-year-long%20civil%20war%20has%20caused%20material%20damage%20of%20nearly%20500%20billion%20dollars.%20All%20this%20notwithstanding%2C%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad's%20government%20has%20tenaciously%20survived%20so%20far%2C%20thanks%20largely%20to%20robust%20military%20assistance%20from%20Russia%2C%20Iran%20and%20Lebanon's%20Hezbollah%20militia.%20His%20regime%20has%20been%20in%20control%20of%20most%20of%20the%20country%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20keeping%20at%20bay%20at%20least%2049%20militias%2C%20mostly%20Sunni%20outfits%20holed%20up%20in%20a%204%20million-strong%20Idlib%20exclusion%20zone%20in%20the%20northwest%20bordering%20Turkey%2C%20which%20protects%20them.%20The%20instability%20in%20Iraq%2C%20Lebanon%20and%20Gaza%20has%20also%20permeated%20into%20Syria.%20While%20projecting%20%26quot%3Brejectionism%26quot%3B%20against%20Israel%2C%20Damascus%20has%20been%20careful%20to%20avoid%20a%20direct%20military%20confrontation%20despite%20frequent%20air%20attacks.%20After%20being%20ostracised%20by%20the%20Arab%20League%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20it%20was%20invited%20to%20rejoin%20the%20regional%20body.%20Most%20of%20the%20Arab%20countries%20have%20resumed%20diplomatic%20ties%20with%20Syria%2C%20even%20as%20Western%20sanctions%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpasm%20Of%20Sunni%20Salafism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunni%20militancy%20has%20been%20endemic%20to%20Syria.%20But%20lately%2C%20an%20eerie%20pattern%20seems%20to%20have%20set%20in%3A%20the%20sudden%20and%20periodic%20spasms%20of%20Sunni%20Salafism%20every%20decade%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years%3A%20in%202004%20it%20was%20affected%20by%20the%20scourge%20of%20al-Qaeda%20in%20neighbouring%20Iraq%2C%20only%20to%20be%20snuffed%20out%20two%20years%20later%20by%20the%20occupying%20US%20forces%20there.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20infamous%20Islamic%20State%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%20(ISIS)%20under%20self-styled%20Khalifa%20Abu%20Bakr%20al-Baghdadi%20exploded%20with%20a%20mysterious%20and%20gruesome%20mix%20of%20modern%20military%20hardware%20and%20regressive%20theocracy.%20The%20ISIS%20quickly%20overran%20a%20swathe%20of%20territory%20bigger%20than%20France%20with%20Raqqah%20as%20its%20capital%20and%20annual%20revenue%20of%20over%20a%20billion%20dollars.%20After%20earning%20notoriety%20for%20its%20medieval%20conduct%2C%20it%20too%20was%20militarily%20vanquished%20in%202019%20by%20an%20unlikely%20coalition%20of%20Iran%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Iraqi%20Shia%20and%20Kurdish%20militias.%20Though%20it%20lost%20all%20territorial%20control%2C%20it%20still%20managed%20some%20spectacular%20operations%20hitting%20Moscow%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20after%20ISIS%2C%20the%20HTS%20led%20by%20Abu%20Mohammad%20al-Julani%20emerged%20out%20of%20the%20shadows%20on%20November%2027%202024%2C%20waging%20a%20blitzkrieg%20to%20shatter%20the%20wobbly%20peace%20of%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20Within%20a%20week%2C%20it%20has%20occupied%20Aleppo%20and%20Hama%2C%20Syria's%20second%20and%20fourth%20largest%20cities.%20The%20HTS%20leads%20a%20motley%20Sunni%20rebel%20coalition%20poised%20to%20march%20on%20to%20Homs%20and%20threaten%20Damascus.%20In%20tandem%20with%20its%20advance%2C%20the%20Kurdish%20Self-Defence%20Force%20in%20the%20northeast%20and%20the%20Druze%20population%20in%20the%20south%20have%20also%20asserted%20against%20the%20central%20authority.%20Despite%20HTS%20claims%20of%20coordination%2C%20the%20actions%20by%20Kurdish%20and%20Druze%20elements%20appear%20autonomous%20and%20opportunistic.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Emergence%20Of%20The%20HTS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pattern%20is%20hardly%20coincidental.%20These%20perennial%20ethnic%20frictions%20manifest%20at%20opportune%20times%20of%20weak%20and%20unpopular%20regimes%2C%20social%20vacuum%20and%20external%20sponsors.%20The%20violent%20and%20toxic%20movements%20seek%20legitimacy%20through%20tactical%20shifts%20and%20the%20use%20of%20religious%20and%20sectarian%20symbols%2C%20but%20generate%20more%20heat%20than%20light%20and%20are%20eventually%20consumed%20by%20their%20overreach%20and%20overzealousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emergence%20of%20the%20HTS%20has%20followed%20this%20script.%20It%20sensed%20opportunity%20as%20the%20Syrian%20army%20was%20exhausted%20after%2013%20years%20of%20unrelenting%20civil%20war%20and%20persistent%20Israeli%20air%20attacks.%20The%20lack%20of%20any%20peace%20dividend%20and%20political%20reforms%20has%20left%20the%20population%20disgruntled.%20Equally%20importantly%2C%20Iran%20and%20Russia%2C%20Damascus'%20powerful%20external%20backers%2C%20each%20currently%20have%20their%20well-known%20preoccupations.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HTS%20seems%20to%20have%20internalised%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20previous%20two%20Salafi%20insurrections.%20It%20has%20tried%20to%20cobble%20together%20a%20wider%20coalition%20of%20Sunni%20militias%20shunning%2C%20at%20least%20temporarily%2C%20the%20Salafi%20dogma%20it%20inherited%20from%20Al-Nusra%20Front%2C%20its%20al-Qaeda-aligned%20previous%20Avatar.%20It%20has%20also%20sought%20to%20have%20a%20modus%20vivendi%20with%20minorities%20such%20as%20Druze%2C%20Christians%2C%20Kurds%2C%20etc.%20Although%20proscribed%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20the%20UN%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Turkey%20etc.%2C%20it%20has%2C%20reportedly%2C%20been%20sustained%20by%20Ankara%20and%20Doha.%20Possible%20crowdfunding%20from%20other%20sources%2C%20including%20Syrians%20in%20exile%20(over%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20total%20population)%20as%20well%20as%20private%20largesse%20from%20the%20various%20Sunni%20outfits%20and%20non-state%20actors%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBashar%20al-Assad%20Has%20Held%20On%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20HTS'%20initial%20shock%20successes%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20is%20too%20early%20to%20count%20out%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad%2C%20who%20has%20long%20defied%20prophesies%20of%20his%20demise.%20His%20battle-hardened%20and%20well-equipped%20army%20and%20security%20agencies%20are%20motivated%20by%20hard%20back-to-a-wall%20survival%20instinct.%20While%20his%20popularity%20is%20uncertain%2C%20he%20has%20provided%20a%20modicum%20of%20stability%20to%20the%20country%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20So%2C%20for%20many%20in%20Syria%2C%20as%20a%20familiar%20devil%2C%20he%20may%20be%20preferable%20to%20unpredictable%20vendetta-driven%20revolutionaries.%20If%20push%20came%20to%20shove%20and%20Russia%20and%20Iran%20proved%20unwilling%20or%20unable%20to%20help%20out%20this%20time%2C%20the%20al-Assad%20clan%20retains%20the%20manoeuvrability%20to%20find%20new%20saviours.%20His%20last%20calling%20card%20would%20be%20that%20only%20he%20can%20keep%20Syria%20together%20and%20moderate%20(notwithstanding%20the%20fiery%20rhetoric)%20and%20his%20departure%20could%20lead%20to%20anarchy%20in%20a%20fragmented%20country%20with%20warring%20sectarian%20cantons%20that%20would%20make%20Lebanon%20appear%20as%20an%20oasis%20of%20peace.%20%C2%A0While%20quite%20a%20few%20of%20his%20internal%20and%20external%20detractors%20may%20not%20mind%20a%20regime%20change%2C%20very%20few%20of%20them%2C%20including%20the%20Western%20countries%2C%20Israel%20and%20Turkey%2C%20would%20countenance%20risking%20Syria%20being%20fractured%20into%20mutually%20warring%20cantons%20along%20ethnic%20or%20religious%20lines.%20The%20bitter%20legacy%20of%20the%2013%20years%20of%20civil%20war%20has%20thwarted%20the%20success%20of%20numerous%20attempts%20at%20reconciling%20the%20al-Assad%20regime%20with%20its%20militant%20opponents%2C%20notably%20through%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20the%20Asthana%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20run%2C%20thus%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bmother%20of%20all%20battles%26quot%3B%20is%20shaping%20up%20to%20control%20crucial%20central%20highlands%20around%20the%20Hama-Homs%20axis.%20To%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20its%20outcome%20would%20depend%20on%20which%20of%20the%20two%20sides%20would%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20their%20flock%20together%20and%20marshal%20their%20respective%20sponsors'%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20flux%20in%20Syria%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20the%20aftershocks%20of%20Israel's%20pyrrhic%20but%20decisive%20victory%20over%20Hamas%20and%20Hezbollah%20during%20the%20preceding%20weeks.%20It%20may%20also%20be%20a%20forerunner%20for%20an%20eventual%20epic%20confrontation%20between%20Israel%20and%20Iran%20if%20Tehran%20loses%20Syria%2C%20its%20last%20perch%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Badvance%20defence%20strategy%26quot%3B%20against%20Israel.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20India%20Should%20Be%20Concerned%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20India%20may%20be%20physically%20distant%20from%20Syria's%20killing%20fields%2C%20several%20factors%20cast%20a%20long%20shadow%20upon%20us.%20Firstly%2C%20while%20Syria%20itself%20is%20not%20an%20oil%20and%20gas%20exporter%2C%20it%20lies%20close%20to%20the%20Gulf%2C%20which%20has%20major%20oil%20and%20gas%20reserves.%20Consequently%2C%20developments%20there%20are%20strategically%20important%20for%20us%20for%20several%20reasons%2C%20such%20as%20our%20hydrocarbon%20source%2C%20the%20base%20for%20over%209%20million%20Indian%20expatriates%2C%20remittances%20and%20the%20export%20market.%20Protracted%20instability%20in%20Syria%20can%20therefore%20affect%20our%20vital%20interests.%20%C2%A0It%20is%20less%20well%20known%20that%20over%204%20million%20Indians%2C%20mostly%20Malayalis%2C%20belong%20to%20the%20Syrian%20Christian%20church%2C%20constituting%20more%20than%20half%20of%20its%20global%20adherents.%20This%20symbiotic%20confessional%20connection%20makes%20them%20important%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20emerging%20imbroglio.%20Thirdly%2C%20the%20last%20time%20Syria%20faced%20a%20similar%20Salafi%20breakout%20by%20ISIS%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20it%20%26quot%3Binspired%26quot%3B%20a%20small%20but%20significant%20segment%20of%20Indian%20Muslims.%20%C2%A0Some%20even%20answered%20its%20siren%20call%20to%20travel%20to%20Syria%20to%20join%20ISIS%20as%20Jihadis.%20A%20few%20cases%20of%20terror%20perpetrated%20in%20India%20were%20eventually%20traced%20to%20ISIS%20instigation.%20A%20bout%20of%20instability%20in%20Syria%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20conducive%20to%20India's%20security%20and%20domestic%20stability.%20%C2%A0All%20these%20aspects%20enjoin%20us%20to%20keep%20a%20careful%20watch%20on%20the%20ongoing%20Syrian%20developments%20and%20act%20preventively%20to%20safeguard%20our%20national%20interests.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20retired%20Indian%20Ambassador%20who%20learnt%20the%20Arabic%20language%20in%20Damascus.%20He%20currently%20heads%20Eco-Diplomacy%20and%20Strategies%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20consultancy.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733566560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fsigfteag_syria-islamist-rebel-forces-afp_625x300_07_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fan-endgame-in-syria-7193767%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deep-rooted%20structural%20factors%20make%20Syria%20prone%20to%20sudden%20convulsions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20recent%20emergence%20of%20Hai'at%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS%2C%20in%20English%20Syria%20Liberation%20Organisation).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fan-endgame-in-syria-7193767%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Annapurna%20Finance%20raises%20%24109.5%20mn%20via%20multilateral%20ECB%20transactions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733566315000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fannapurna-finance-raises-109-5-mn-via-multilateral-ecb-transactions-124120700379_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20funds%20have%20been%20raised%20from%2010%20known%20financial%20institutions%20from%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20Africa%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Paris%20fell%20silent%20when%20Notre-Dame%20went%20up%20in%20flames%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733565300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F11%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-notre-dame-cathedral_6760910.jpg%3F20241206170816%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhow-paris-fell-silent-when-notre-dame-went-up-in-flames-13268506%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ps