0regained%20mobile%20connectivity%20and%20contacted%20emergency%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Belagavi%20police%20control%20room%20passed%20the%20information%20to%20the%20Khanapur%20police%2C%20who%20used%20GPS%20coordinates%20to%20locate%20the%20family%20and%20reach%20them%20with%20the%20help%20of%20villagers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Nayak%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20further%20mentioned%20that%20the%20family%20was%20fortunate%20to%20find%20mobile%20connectivity%2C%20as%20the%20forest%20is%20home%20to%20diverse%20wildlife%2C%20with%20a%20recent%20bear%20attack%20in%20the%20area%20leaving%20a%20farmer%20seriously%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Google%20Maps%20has%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20inaccurate%20information.%20In%20late%20November%2C%20the%20authorities%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20Google%20Maps%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-maps-vows-cooperation-with-authorities-after-misdirection-kills-3-7115630%5C%22%3Ethree%20men%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20their%20car%20drove%20off%20an%20incomplete%20bridge%20while%20following%20a%20route%20suggested%20by%20the%20app.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20as%20the%20group%20was%20heading%20to%20a%20wedding%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Police%20reported%20that%20the%20driver%2C%20relying%20on%20Google%20Maps%2C%20drove%20the%20car%20off%20the%20bridge%20and%20into%20a%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBefore%20that%2C%20in%20August%202024%2C%20a%20X%20user%2C%20Ashish%20Kacholia%2C%20shared%20his%20experience%20after%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fx-user-blames-google-maps-for-missing-bengaluru-to-mumbai-flight-see-post-6457627%5C%22%3Emissed%20a%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20Mumbai%20due%20to%20the%20app's%20flawed%20prediction.%20Mr