wly%20constituted%20288-member%20Maharashtra%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20which%20began%20today.%20The%20session%2C%20overseen%20by%20pro-tem%20Speaker%20Kalidas%20Kolambkar%2C%20includes%20the%20oath%20administration%20for%20MLAs%2C%20the%20election%20of%20the%20assembly%20Speaker%2C%20a%20trust%20vote%20for%20the%20new%20government%2C%20and%20an%20address%20by%20the%20Governor.%20Mr%20Kolambkar%2C%20a%20senior%20BJP%20MLA%2C%20was%20appointed%20pro-tem%20Speaker%20by%20Governor%20CP%20Radhakrishnan%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMVA%20leaders%20gathered%20near%20the%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20statue%20at%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20to%20explain%20their%20stance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20boycotted%20the%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20today%20as%20democracy%20is%20being%20murdered%20by%20the%20use%20of%20EVMs.%20This%20(the%20results%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections)%20is%20not%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20public%20it%20is%20the%20mandate%20of%20EVM%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20senior%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20including%20Nana%20Patole%20of%20Congress%20and%20Jitendra%20Awhad%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20echoed%20concerns%20over%20what%20they%20termed%20an%20%26quot%3Bundemocratic%20attitude%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20and%20reiterated%20demands%20for%20elections%20to%20be%20conducted%20using%20ballot%20papers%20instead%20of%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20results%20have%20raised%20questions%2C%20the%20entire%20process%20seems%20tainted.%20People%20are%20unhappy%2C%20and%20something%20appears%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20alleged%20Congress%20MLA%20Vijay%20Wadettiwar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahayuti%20alliance%2C%20comprising%20the%20BJP%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%2C%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20faction%2C%20won%20230%20of%20the%20288%20assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20November%2020%20elections.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20swearing-in%20of%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20with%20Mr%20Shinde%20and%20Mr%20Pawar%20taking%20oath%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20on%20December%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20dismissed%20the%20Opposition's%20allegations%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20approach%20the%20Election%20Commission%20or%20courts%20with%20evidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20point%20in%20making%20such%20allegations%20here.%20The%20Opposition%20should%20go%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20if%20they%20do%20not%20get%20justice%20there%2C%20they%20should%20approach%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20week-long%20suspense%20over%20the%20Mahayuti's%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20had%20prompted%20Mr%20Thackeray%20to%20label%20the%20delay%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Binsult%20to%20Maharashtra.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20coalition%20took%20over%20a%20week%20after%20the%20results%20to%20decide%20on%20a%20chief%20minister%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20delay%20and%20lack%20of%20transparency%20undermined%20democratic%20principles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20also%20targeted%20the%20BJP's%20decision%20to%20announce%20the%20swearing-in%20date%20before%20formally%20staking%20claim%20to%20form%20the%20government%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Banarchy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRules%20seem%20to%20apply%20only%20to%20opposition%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20MLAs%20had%20also%20quit%20the%20Mahayuti's%20grand%20swearing-in%20ceremony%2C%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20a%20host%20of%20dignitaries%2C%20including%20Union%20ministers%20and%20NDA%20state%20leaders%2C%20at%20Mumbai's%20Azad%20Maidan%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20event%20also%20featured%20celebrities%20from%20Bollywood%2C%20cricket%2C%20and%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733563020000%2C%22v