%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fblack-friday_n_67498606e4b082d91c97359f%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fblack-friday_n_67498606e4b082d91c97359f%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Pollution%20Crisis%3A%20Can%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20Green%20Urban%20Planning%20Offer%20a%20Solution%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20at%20the%20onset%20of%20winter%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20capital%20city%20is%20engulfed%20in%20a%20haze%20strong%20enough%20to%20leave%20its%20residents%20homebound.%20On%2012%20November%2C%202024%2C%20the%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%20reached%20an%20alarming%201%2C200%2C%20with%20new%20reports%20warning%20that%20breathing%20in%20Delhi%20during%20this%20time%20is%20the%20same%20as%20smoking%20over%2040%20cigarettes%20a%20day!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reality%20is%20that%20this%20region%20actually%20has%20a%20high%20level%20of%20pollution%20all%20through%20the%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vimlendu%20Jha%2C%20an%20environmentalist%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Swechha%2C%20a%20youth-run%20NGO%20that%20focuses%20on%20environmental%20issues%20and%20education.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20baseline%20for%20pollution%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20is%20high%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20almost%20always%20above%20250.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20Delhi%20is%20not%20the%20only%20city%20battling%20pollution.%20The%20Indian%20subcontinent%2C%20including%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20Nepal%2C%20hosts%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20polluted%20cities%2C%20far%20exceeding%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%E2%80%99s%20safe%20limit%20of%2050%20%C2%B5g%2Fm%C2%B3%20for%20particulate%20matter%20(a%20mixture%20of%20solid%20particles%20and%20liquid%20droplets%20in%20the%20air).%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20have%20private%20solutions%20to%20public%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAir%20pollution%20can%20on